HEADWORD: Monogenism
<hw>Mo*nog"e*nism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Anthropol.)</fld> <def>The theory or doctrine that the human races
have a common origin, or constitute a single species.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Monogenist</ent>⟦br⟧
